WEBVTT

00:02.920 --> 00:04.160
Several more years passed

00:04.600 --> 00:07.320
You expanded the harem more than tenfold

00:07.840 --> 00:09.160
Nightly revelry

00:09.200 --> 00:11.400
You gradually began to neglect state affairs

00:11.760 --> 00:13.720
When drunk with warm fragrance and soft jade

00:13.920 --> 00:14.920
You strictly ordered

00:15.080 --> 00:17.400
No one is allowed to disturb

00:25.440 --> 00:25.960
Your Highness

00:25.960 --> 00:27.400
Your Highness, you cannot enter

00:29.160 --> 00:29.880
Your Majesty

00:31.400 --> 00:32.120
What are you doing?

00:32.920 --> 00:33.680
Sikong Sheng, what are you doing?

00:33.680 --> 00:34.680
Wretched woman who brings disaster to the state

00:34.680 --> 00:35.440
Your Majesty

00:40.120 --> 00:41.240
Sikong Sheng

00:42.160 --> 00:43.120
What are you doing?

00:45.480 --> 00:46.720
Are you rebelling?

00:47.320 --> 00:48.120
Father

00:49.120 --> 00:50.880
Your son was ordered to oversee the state

00:52.360 --> 00:54.080
But if you continue like this

00:54.240 --> 00:55.400
The state will cease to be a state

00:58.440 --> 00:59.400
Your son

00:59.960 --> 01:01.480
Requests Father to abdicate
